Package net.groboclown.retval.monitor

Class MockCheckMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.groboclown.retval.monitor.CheckMonitor
      • net.groboclown.retval.monitor.MockCheckMonitor
  • public class MockCheckMonitor
extends CheckMonitor
    A mock check monitor, suitable for testing. Note that if used in a non-test environment, this has the potential to quickly consume lots of memory.
